                        <p><b>Course Description:</b></p><p>This course provides the detailed idea about fields of robotics and its control mechanisms.</p><p><b>Course Objective:</b></p><p>The main objective is to provide information on various parts of robots and idea on fields of</p><p>robotics. It also focuses on various kinematics and inverse kinematics of robots, trajectory</p><p>planning of robots and to study the control of robots for some specific applications.</p>
